We are going to add the javscript code @ the end of the html file (not seperate file)

##Buttons - all buttons have class "btn"

Button classes: 
0-9: "btn-primary number" 
+,-,*,/, : "btn-danger operator"
=: "btn-success equal"
clear: "clear"

##Result table: split into 3 h1 headers

id's:
"#first-number"
"#operator"
"#second-number"
"#result"

##Design

Messing with data 
1.Create an event listner for any class btn
2.If-number, operator, or =
3.while(button.class!=operator){ save all inputs into a number }
4.data: firstNumber =""; secondNumber=""; operator ="";



